{"tid":709110,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今年世界盃都一定係巴西拎硬，都唔明其他隊咁努力為咩，損人不利己","createTime":"2018-06-19T17:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T18:28:21.000Z","uid":149955,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd72b4b357d19bf4622e6a81bd194cc5b4d93ee0","tid":709110,"uid":149955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"其實今年世界盃都一定係巴西拎硬，都唔明其他隊咁努力為咩，損人不利己<br />\n<br />\n前鋒已經有兩個球王級，係歐聯同美斯平分秋色既金章安Willian ， 又有曾經既美斯好拍擋屁馬，仲未計耶蘇<br />\n<br />\n中場三個有古世三，世界第一防中不死人，中超球王及應屆西甲冠軍中場保連奴，黃金中場線仲要當打，唔似德國d 老野跑唔郁<br />\n<br />\n後防又有世界第一左閘馬些路，世界第一中堅T Sliva（過去式），係橙汁同Danlio弱少少姐<br />\n<br />\n門將方面，連英超冠軍級神龍Ederson都要做後備，正選艾利臣唔洗我講都知又係一線頭啦<br />\n<br />\n嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n成隊都一線，黃金板凳 廢躝癲佬，廢明奴，F. Luis， Costa 都廢時提啦<br />\n<br />\n冠軍就拎硬架啦，係睇下心情好唔好，炒你幾多粒架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3f797851d22a8c09a4dc0194eb628c273649e9","tid":709110,"uid":149955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T18:02:35.000Z","msg":"觀迎 binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b722d297110bec923d73b9e38db55e3de9c1958","tid":709110,"uid":35176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T18:04:23.000Z","msg":"算吧啦巴西 有外星人C朗拿度<br />\n巴西等收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f8df2e75ab4648c61398754232ead002a0a1ab","tid":709110,"uid":149955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b722d297110bec923d73b9e38db55e3de9c1958","tid":709110,"uid":35176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T18:04:23.000Z","msg":"算吧啦巴西 有外星人C朗拿度<br />\n巴西等收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" clas